These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia, daffodil
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Flower   | marigold | begonia | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, turkish, dutch
1. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the dutch is in the middle##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Nationality   | italian | dutch | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | musical | zombie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, lizard
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Pet   | rabbit | turtle | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
