.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, yellow, light-blue
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Color   | lavender | yellow | light-blue |

