.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
House: ranch-style, futuristic, farmhouse
1. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
2. the farmhouse house is between the futuristic house and the ranch-style house##2
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse | ranch-style |

